. Design
. There are total 3 files 2 source file and 1 header file.

main.cc: 
. mainly contains the general code, such as userinput parsing & then calling the appropriote function. 

functions.cc:
. Contains all the implementations of the algorithms requred for this algorithm
	Mthod readBit and writeBit are taken for earlier DES assignment

	BIGNUM library is extensively used in this project

functions.h
. Contains the prototype declarations of all the functions defined in functions.cc
it also contains the round macro, given to us in the homework specification page


